WEBVTT

00:07:57.593 --> 00:08:00.776
And I freed myself
from the fear of judgment

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:03.680
from the one person who I thought
would judge me the most --

00:08:04.109 --> 00:08:05.259
my son,

00:08:05.847 --> 00:08:07.839
who actually told me,

00:08:07.863 --> 00:08:11.736
"Mom, you are the strongest
person that I know.

00:08:12.117 --> 00:08:13.784
You can get through this.

00:08:14.427 --> 00:08:19.164
And besides, mom -- he chose
the wrong woman to mess with."

00:08:19.188 --> 00:08:20.904
(Laughter)

00:08:20.928 --> 00:08:25.544
(Applause)

00:08:25.568 --> 00:08:29.262
It was on that day that I decided
to use my platform

00:08:29.286 --> 00:08:31.785
and my story and my voice.